All Nippon Names Iwakata President of AirAsia Japan Budget Unit

-- B y   C h r i s   C o o p e r   a n d   K i y o t a k a   M a t s u d a
-- 
2011-08-31T06:00:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/all-nippon-names-iwakata-president-of-airasia-japan-budget-unit.html
All Nippon Airways Co.,  Japan ’s
largest listed carrier, named Kazuyuki Iwakata president of its
new budget carrier AirAsia Japan Co.  The carrier, which is forming the unit with Malaysia’s
 AirAsia Bhd. (AIRA) , set up AirAsia Japan today and plans to start
flights from August 2012, it said in a statement released in
 Tokyo  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chris Cooper in Tokyo at 
 ccooper1@bloomberg.net ;
Kiyotaka Matsuda in Tokyo at 
 kmatsuda@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Neil Denslow at 
 ndenslow@bloomberg.net  